1832944,"uid":222499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"炒貴刁最正係有螄蚶，可惜香港好難搵到有螄蚶嘅炒貴刁"},{"pid":"96b269dbeccc2c25473e050c5220315475774b5b","tid":1832944,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"I heartily recommend the restaurant in Gold hotel Taipei. It has an unusual menu. It serves a buffet breakfast and a breakfast with a choice of menu. For lunch there're a buffet lunch and two set menus of three courses. It also offers a buffet supper and a menu of four courses. I ordered beef served with onions from the menu while my cousin's husband chose a vegetable dish from the menu. The inside of the meat is raw whereas the outer surface is cooked. Onions can be eaten raw or cooked. The cafe in the hotel also has an excellent menu. I made a table reservation at the cafe for two people for quarter after seven next Saturday."},{"pid":"d23e85780ec072c02af0786ffed3070b850ddb80","tid":1832944,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"良友快餐"},{"pid":"d2c696c97ca6a5fe58c4452e59b7bc9f62a5e169","tid":1832944,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02999daf9bf4650412e078e7fc70c9ef0a555032","tid":1832944,"uid":161462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"有無唔辣嘅炒貴刁<br />\n我個仔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:36:37.000Z","msg":"炒河粉"},{"pid":"ef830d8db5bf343d93982972a9f00f5b6bf33487","tid":1832944,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"Cafe Malacca"}]}